  • Package org.thewhitemage13.dto

    • Class org.thewhitemage13.dto.CreateUserDTO

      class CreateUserDTO extends Object implements Serializable

      • Serialized Fields

        • email
          @NotBlank(message="Email is required") @Email(message="Invalid email format") String email
          The email address of the user.

          Must be in a valid email format.

        • firstName
          @NotBlank(message="First name is required") @Size(max=50,message="First name must not exceed 50 characters") String firstName
          The first name of the user.

          Cannot exceed 50 characters.

        • lastName
          @Size(max=50,message="Last name must not exceed 50 characters") String lastName
          The last name of the user.

          Optional field but cannot exceed 50 characters if provided.

        • password
          @NotBlank(message="Password is required") @Size(min=8,message="Password must be at least 8 characters long") String password
          The password for the user's account.

          Must be at least 8 characters long.

        • phoneNumber
          @Pattern(regexp="^\\+?[0-9]{10,15}$",message="Phone number must be valid and contain 10 to 15 digits") String phoneNumber
          The phone number of the user.

          Must contain 10 to 15 digits and can include an optional "+" prefix.

        • profilePictureUrl
          @Pattern(regexp="^(http|https)://.*",message="Profile picture URL must be a valid URL") String profilePictureUrl
          The profile picture URL of the user.

          Must be a valid HTTP or HTTPS URL.

        • region
          @NotBlank(message="Region is required") String region
          The region associated with the user.

          Cannot be blank.

        • surname
          @Size(max=50,message="Surname must not exceed 50 characters") String surname
          The surname of the user.

          Optional field but cannot exceed 50 characters if provided.

        • username
          @NotBlank(message="Username is required") @Size(min=3,max=50,message="Username must be between 3 and 50 characters") String username
          The username of the user.

          Must be between 3 and 50 characters in length.
